<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.8">
<l>kaṟṟārpaṟ ṟaṟukkum piṟavip peruṅkaṭalē</l>
<l>paṟṟāvan taṭiyēṉ piṟantēṉ piṟantapiṉṉai</l>
<l>vaṟṟānīr vayalcūḻ vayalā liyammāṉaip</l>
<l>peṟṟēṉpeṟ ṟatuvum piṟavā maipeṟṟēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was born a servant, arriving [all the] while grasping for</l>
<l>The great sea of births whose bonds the wise break. After [my] birth,</l>
<l>I attained the lord of Vayalāli encircled by fields of undiminishing waters.</l>
<l>As soon as [I] attained him, I attained birthlessness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
